变形由 $x_{1}=\lambda_{1}X_{1}$，$x_{2}=\lambda_{2}X_{2}$，$x_{3}=\lambda_{3}X_{3}$ 给出。变形梯度张量 $F$ 的分量为 $F_{iJ}=\frac{\partial x_{i}}{\partial X_{J}}$。计算偏导数可得
$$
F=\begin{pmatrix}
\frac{\partial x_{1}}{\partial X_{1}} & \frac{\partial x_{1}}{\partial X_{2}} & \frac{\partial x_{1}}{\partial X_{3}}\\
\frac{\partial x_{2}}{\partial X_{1}} & \frac{\partial x_{2}}{\partial X_{2}} & \frac{\partial x_{2}}{\partial X_{3}}\\
\frac{\partial x_{3}}{\partial X_{1}} & \frac{\partial x_{3}}{\partial X_{2}} & \frac{\partial x_{3}}{\partial X_{3}}
\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_{1} & 0 & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{2} & 0\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{3}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$
左柯西-格林变形张量定义为 $B=F F^{T}$。由于 $F$ 是对角矩阵，所以 $F^{T}=F$，乘积得到
$$
B=F F^{T}=\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_{1} & 0 & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{2} & 0\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{3}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_{1} & 0 & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{2} & 0\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{3}
\end{pmatrix}
=\begin{pmatrix}
\lambda_{1}^{2} & 0 & 0\\
0 & \lambda_{2}^{2} & 0\\
0 & 0 & \lambda_{3}^{2}
\end{pmatrix}.
$$
因此，$B$ 的矩阵表示是一个对角矩阵，其对角线上的元素为 $\lambda_{1}^{2}$、$\lambda_{2}^{2}$ 和 $\lambda_{3}^{2}$。
